query:
UPDATE nozzleEvaluations 
SET minimumRequired = CASE nozzleNumber
  WHEN 'N1' THEN 0.1348
  WHEN 'N2' THEN 0.1164
  WHEN 'N3' THEN 0.1164
  WHEN 'N4' THEN 0.1890
  WHEN 'N5' THEN 0.2450
  WHEN 'N6' THEN 0.2074
  WHEN 'N7' THEN 0.1348
  WHEN 'N8' THEN 0.1269
  WHEN 'N9' THEN 0.4918
END,
acceptable = 1,
updatedAt = NOW()
WHERE inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber = '57-11-001')
AND nozzleNumber IN ('N1','N2','N3','N4','N5','N6','N7','N8','N9');
